<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <p>Hi there,</p>

    <p>Thanks for giving PodRead a try. I'm a solo dev working on this on nights and weekends and as more customers have come on board, I've had to update the pricing model.</p>

    <p>Credits used to be $1 each. They're $2 now. Long articles over 20,000 characters with a Premium voice cost 2 credits instead of 1. Everything else still costs 1.</p>

    <p>You bought credits under the old price (thank you!). I doubled your balance and added 20 credits on top. You went from <%= @previous_balance %> to <%= @new_balance %>.</p>

    <p>Thanks again for using PodRead.</p>

    <p>
      Jesse<br>
      jesse@podread.app
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
